title: Second Date Update: Experiment Gone Wrong
itunes:title: Second Date Update: Experiment Gone Wrong
description: We didn't want to do it, but in today's Second Date Update we banned our first listener from appearing on the show ever again. We warned them… we tried to stop them… but they went there and we had to take extreme measures.
